    Frequently Asked Questions

    Do you have any questions? Contact us at: info@wecreativelab.com

    Upon purchase, you'll receive instant access to the planners through a secure online link or downloadable file. Simply follow the provided instructions to start your download.

    Yes, you can by purchasing the Master Resell Rights version, which includes the license and is currently available for a limited time. With this version, you'll gain direct access to all planner templates on Canva, including over 1500 pages of templates.

    Our planners is compatible with various devices, including computers, tablets, and smartphones. Access and organize your plans anytime, anywhere!

    If you want to write on the planners through your device, you can use any PDF annotation app such as Goodnotes, Notability, Samsung Notes, Collanotes, Xodo, and more. It works smoothly on both iOS and Android systems, making it easy to use on your preferred device. For editing the templates, you can edit them using Canva.

    This collection is different from the Mystic Bundle. While some bonus planners are included in both collections, the majority of the planners here focus on mental health and personal growth, offering unique themes not found in the Mystic Bundle.

    No problem! You can simply download the planners and print them with a printer, or use them on your preferred devices such as iPad, tablet, computer, and phone!

    These planners are 100% editable to match your style. Add your logo, change fonts, insert your photos, modify text, adjust formats, and much more.

    You don't need a Canva Pro account to edit the templates; you can customize them with the free plan. Note that some planners include both free and pro elements. If you have a free account, simply replace or remove the pro elements with free ones before downloading the files. This way, you won't have to pay for premium graphic elements.

    All the planners are in PDF format, ready to be downloaded and printed or used on your devices.

    No, this is a digital product. After purchase, you will immediately receive all the planners via email!

    If you've purchased "The Planner Boutique Full Collection" or "The Planner Luxe," these planners are already included.

    The digital products offered on this site do not provide professional advice and are not intended to replace consultation with experts.
